---
// src/pages/specials.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="特展 - 寂静画廊">
  <h1>特展收藏</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">这里是画廊不定期推出的、关于特定主题的策展系列。</p>

  <div class="special-list">
    <a href="/specials/monthly-finds" class="special-card">
      <h2>月度新发现</h2>
      <p>追踪策展人最新发现的、充满时效性的展品清单。</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/specials/pantheon-movies" class="special-card">
      <h2>电影封神榜</h2>
      <p>那些经过时间考验的、定义了本画廊审美基石的影像作品。</p>
    </a>
    <!-- 未来你可以继续在这里添加新的特展链接 -->
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: #666;
    margin-top: -1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .special-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .special-card {
    display: block;
    background-color: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .special-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .special-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .special-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #666;
  }
</style>